.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, disco, blues, salsa, trance
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, lacrosse, biathlon, volleyball, snowboarding
City: hamburg, liverpool, rome, miami, berlin
1. the british is the person who likes red
2. the swedish is the person traveling to rome
3. the danish is the fan of salsa
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the fan of disco
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person traveling to liverpool
7. the person who likes yellow is the person who's sport is lacrosse
8. the fan of blues is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg
11. the person traveling to berlins is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse
12. the person who's sport is basketball is the fan of punk
13. the german is the person who's sport is volleyball
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the fan of trance

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| City		|     hamburg	|    berlin	|     liverpool	|     miami	|      rome	|
| Music-Genre	|    trance	|     salsa	|     blues	|    disco	|      punk	|
| Sport		|   lacrosse	|    snowboarding	|  biathlon	|    volleyball	|   basketball	|
